      <Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="Number">69</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">한국</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">펫 전문몰</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">펫프렌즈</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">https://www.pet-friends.co.kr</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">반려동물 상품몰</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">품종/나이/건강상태/사료 조건 검색</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">B</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">반려동물 특성 기반 상품 검색은 AI 추천 가치가 큽니다.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">전문몰 확장 후보</Data></Cell></Row>
